  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ceramic tagine over medium heat.",
    "Add the lamb pieces and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in the ground cumin and smoked paprika and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the low sodium chicken broth and tomato paste and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped Thai sweet basil and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Serve the harira hot, garnished with additional basil if desired."
